# AIGOS — Strategic Marketing Blueprint Generator

Stack: Next.js 15, Vercel AI SDK v6, Anthropic Claude, Supabase (DB + realtime), Clerk auth, Railway worker.

## Architecture

The journey is FORM-DRIVEN, not chat-driven. No AI asks questions. No chat-based onboarding.

User flow:
1. Enter URL -> auto-prefill fields
2. Review/edit in form (UnifiedFieldReview)
3. Submit -> dispatches deepResearchProgram (corpus + onboarding fields)
4. Corpus completes -> workspace opens with the Run section operator control
5. User clicks Run section -> next pending report section dispatches
6. Section completes -> Run section control rotates to the next pending section, ready for the next click
7. User clicks through the pipeline section by section (industryMarket, icpValidation, competitors, offerAnalysis, keywordIntel, crossAnalysis)
8. After the 6 report sections (industryMarket through crossAnalysis): guided prompt for Media Plan
9. After media plan: guided prompt for Scripts
10. All results saved to profile

Progression contract: every report section requires an operator click. The only auto-dispatch is the URL-form deepResearchProgram (step 3). This is the supervised progression locked in the rescue/deep-research-six-cards rescue plan.

Research dispatch: Button clicks -> POST /api/journey/dispatch -> Railway worker -> Supabase -> realtime to frontend.
Chat sidebar: Post-research editing only (editCard, updateField). Does NOT trigger research.

Pipeline: deepResearchProgram -> industryMarket -> icpValidation -> competitors -> offerAnalysis -> keywordIntel -> crossAnalysis -> mediaPlan

## Conventions

- Imports: @/* maps to ./src/* (always absolute)
- UI: shadcn/ui (new-york) + Radix + Tailwind CSS v4. cn() for conditional classes.
- Files: kebab-case. Named exports (not default). Props suffixed with Props.
- All AI calls: @ai-sdk/anthropic directly. Never OpenRouter.
- Zod for all AI outputs and API inputs.

## Gotchas

- id vs run_id: Frontend passes run_id. Query .eq('run_id', id).
- Railway worker (research-worker/) cannot import from src/lib/.
- toUIMessageStreamResponse() requires DefaultChatTransport. Mismatch = silent failure.
- Tool definitions: inputSchema (not parameters), maxOutputTokens (not maxTokens).
- Remove .min()/.max() from Zod numbers in generateObject schemas.
- Read DESIGN.md before any visual/UI work.
